room_title: Escape room " Castle Escape" by Escape Zone 60 in Panama City
room_address: 8128 Front Beach Rd. D Panama City Beach, FL 32407
room_description: Go back to the medieval days when there were castles, dungeons and dragons. You and others are thrown into the dungeon for crimes committed. (wrongly accused we are sure-) In 60 minutes, the torturer will return to do what he does best and you don't want to be there when he returns. Will 60 minutes be enough time for you and your fellow victims to find the clues and solve the puzzles necessary to escape?
